eadquarters in rockefeller center to a unit of mitsui real estate development co ltd in  for  million john walsh president of exxon subsidiary friendswood development company stated that exxon left new york because the costs were too high in  exxon partnered with turner ridge capital management to develop and finance their us alternative energy infastructure in  exxonmobil successfully asked a us federal court to lift the aforementioned trademark injunction that banned it from using the esso brand in various states by this time as a result of numerous mergers and rebranding the remaining standard oil companies that previously objected to the esso name had been acquired by bp exxonmobil cited trademark surveys in which there was no longer possible confusion with the esso name as it was more than seven decades before bp also had no objection to lift the ban exxonmobil did not specify whether they would now open new stations in the us under the esso name they were primarily concerned about the additional expenses of having separate marketing letterheads packaging and other materials that omit esso logoedit the rectangular exxon logo with the blue strip at the bottom and red lettering with the two xs interlinked together was designed by noted industrial stylist raymond loewy the interlinked xs are incorporated in the modernday exxonmobil corporate logo but the original exxon logo continues for marketing and station signage mad magazine spoofed the logo by showing a huge sign above the white house nixxon with the caption but its still the same old gas in  minolta introduced a new autofocus slr camera system named maxxum in the united states originally cameras such as the maxxum  lenses and flashes used a logo with the xs crossed in maxxum exxon considered this a violation of their trademark and as a result minolta was allowed to distribute cameras already produced but was forced to change the stylistic xx and implement this as a change in new production brandingedit exxon is exxonmobils primary retail gasoline brand in most of the united states with the highest concentration of retail outlets located in new jersey pennsylvania texas and in the midatlantic and southeastern states the exxon brand has a significant market presence in the following metropolitan areas map of exxon stores in the united states atlanta new orleans baltimore new york city metro new jersey birmingham philadelphia charlotte pittsburgh chicago dallas raleigh houston richmond memphis virginia beachnorfolknewport news nashville washington dc mobil is the companys primary retail gasoline brand in california florida new york new england the great lakes and the midwest esso is exxonmobils primary gasoline brand worldwide except in australia and new zealand where the mobil brand is used exclusively in colombia both the esso and mobil brands are used referencesedit  exxon corporation encyclopædia britannica retrieved  july    a guide to the exxonmobil historical collection  part  briscoe center for american history the university of texas at austin retrieved  january    exxonmobil  our history retrieved   and see also the fact that almost at newport jazz festival  the musician muddy waters performed his hit put a tiger in your tank slating the esso advert by applying the slogan to special masculinitys sexual wishes towards a woman cf muddy waters  tiger in your tank retrieved   and its recording on the album at newport   as the year of the final slogan message is also mentioned by brian ash tiger in your tank the anatomy of an advertising campaign  p   on with exxon time timecom  retrieved    pearson anne and ralph bivins exxon moving corporate headquarters to dallas houston chronicle friday october   a retrieved on july    the return of esso gasoline csp daily news  february  retrieved  september    after  years exxon asks court to use esso name again csp daily news  december  retrieved  september    minolta maxxum camera with original crossed xx logo  minolta maxxu